episodes.title: Du ser ut som en slut
episodes.plot: Eva in her first year at school and has fallen out with her old friends Ingrid and Sara. She only knows her boyfriend Jonas and his friend Isak at school. She gets convinced to go to school party, where she meets several new people.

episodes.title: Jonas, dette er helt dust
episodes.plot: During fall holiday Eva, Jonas and Isak go on a cabin trip. Eva is annoyed because her boyfriend invited Isak along. The tension between them rises when she suspects Jonas is keeping secrets.

episodes.title: Vi er de største loserne på skolen
episodes.plot: Back at school Eva befriends Noora in her Spanish class. They and Sana gets invited by Vilde and Chris to join them in getting a bus for the graduation celebration when they become "russ" in three years.

episodes.title: Go for it din lille slut
episodes.plot: Sana and Vilde wants Eva to get in touch with Christoffer in the third year, to get them invited to a party with the third year boys, among them the most popular boy in school William.

episodes.title: Hva er det som gjør deg kåt?
episodes.plot: Eva invites Jonas for dinner to meet her mom. Vilde is falling for William, and the girls visits the school doctor to get contraceptives because Vilde has decided she wants to lose her virginity.

episodes.title: Man vet når gutter lyver
episodes.plot: Eva suspects that Jonas is cheating on her with her former friend Ingrid, and meets Isak to talk about it. Vilde reveals details about her and William. The girls go to a Halloween party Christoffer invited them to.

episodes.title: Tenker alltid det er meg det er noe galt med
episodes.plot: After kissing Christoffer on Halloween Eva feels guilty, and asks Isak for counsel. Noora wants Vilde to stand up for herself and stop caring for William after he started ignoring her for other girls.

episodes.title: Hele skolen hater meg
episodes.plot: Everyone knows about what happened on Halloween, and the entire school is gossiping about Eva. Jonas won't talk to her and on top of things Vilde finds out about her past. William starts to show interest for Noora.

episodes.title: Man er det man gjør
episodes.plot: Eva gets a threatening letter, and Vilde decides to leave the bus crew. Eva is thinking about changing to another school, while trying to find out who wrote the letter.

episodes.title: Jeg tenker at du har blitt helt psyko
episodes.plot: The girls start to get worried something is wrong with Vilde. Eva talks with Jonas after not talking for a long time. The girls go to a Christmas party, and Eva decides to confront Isak.

episodes.title: Et jævlig dumt valg
episodes.plot: Vilde reveals that she thinks she may be pregnant. William continues to flirt with Noora. Isak and Eva talk out, and Eva decides to have a heart-to-heart conversation with Jonas.
